Real Madrid coach Zinedine Zidane admits they struggled for their draw with Chelsea. Real Madrid were held 1-1 at Valdebebas for the first-leg of their Champions League draw on Tuesday night. Having to come from behind after conceding early. Zidane insists they showed the right character and spirit after halftime and hailed goalscorer Karim Benzema for again producing at the right moment for Los Merengues.